@Buxaroo, rock100 â€” I've been looking everywhere for serial or some way to install the newest patch (v1.04 now), I couldn't find anything, but I've found a v1.02 patch. Don't remember where I downloaded it from, but search for "Panzer Corps Walthers", and download it from somewhere. You'll find multiple torrents on google... load trackers from all of them if you don't see any seeders. Oh, and if you get the CRC error after extraction, check your PanzerCorps.TXT file and HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Slitherine\PanzerCorps\ "PanzerCorps" key via regedit; they have to contain the same serial (just find the above key with Run+R -> regedit, and change the "PanzerCorps" serial key to 1111-1111-1111-1111).
HTH.

